1
00:00:02,840 --> 00:00:04,760
Miss Feng, do you feel
this secret relationship

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:06,240
is emotionally unfair to you?

3
00:00:06,673 --> 00:00:07,680
Of course not.

4
00:00:08,240 --> 00:00:10,280
Neither of us wants to pressure the other.

5
00:00:10,320 --> 00:00:12,480
This actually keeps us more stable.

6
00:00:13,040 --> 00:00:14,760
Then why go public now?

7
00:00:14,920 --> 00:00:16,560
We got caught during my set visit.

8
00:00:16,600 --> 00:00:18,640
So we just admitted it.

9
00:00:19,080 --> 00:00:21,240
Rumor says Mr. Zhen is shooting a gay film.

10
00:00:21,280 --> 00:00:22,280
And it's pretty bold.

11
00:00:22,360 --> 00:00:23,360
Does that bother you?

12
00:00:23,840 --> 00:00:24,680
Not at all.

13
00:00:24,720 --> 00:00:25,760
It's just acting.

14
00:00:25,960 --> 00:00:28,400
If it weren't a gay film,

15
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:30,360
I might worry more.

16
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:34,000
Have you met his co-star?

17
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:35,840
Mr. Zhang?
I have.

18
00:00:36,760 --> 00:00:38,040
He's really nice.

19
00:00:38,080 --> 00:00:39,400
We even had hot pot together.

20
00:00:41,480 --> 00:00:42,720
Stop watching, bro.

21
00:00:42,920 --> 00:00:43,840
Please, Zhun.
I'm begging you.

22
00:00:44,760 --> 00:00:46,160
Get a grip.

23
00:00:46,760 --> 00:00:49,273
You are just
shooting a gay film.

24
00:00:49,320 --> 00:00:50,360
You're not gay.

25
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:52,280
What about Danyi?

26
00:00:56,160 --> 00:00:57,200
I won't hold her back.

27
00:00:58,560 --> 00:00:59,560
I'll break up with her.

28
00:00:59,840 --> 00:01:00,400
What?

29
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:01,680
Are you crazy?

30
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:04,800
Fine, fine.

31
00:01:05,240 --> 00:01:06,480
Forget gay or not gay.

32
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:08,920
His relationship is already public.

33
00:01:09,080 --> 00:01:10,280
And you still want to dive in?

34
00:01:10,360 --> 00:01:11,600
That's just stupid.

35
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:15,640
My phone.

36
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:20,920
Give me my phone back.

37
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:35,200
Move, please.

38
00:01:36,080 --> 00:01:37,720
Since you went public with Miss Feng,

39
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:38,720
why say your feelings are uncertain?

40
00:01:38,760 --> 00:01:40,760
I don't like the media prying
into my private life.

41
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:44,000
Interviewing me is your job.

42
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:45,920
My love life is mine.

43
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,200
You just admitted you're in love.

44
00:01:50,320 --> 00:01:51,680
Is it not Miss Feng?

45
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:53,680
Sorry,

46
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:55,520
but I don't owe the world every detail.

47
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:57,200
Does that mean in relationships,

48
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:58,760
you're irresponsible?

49
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:01,400
Who am I responsible to?

50
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:04,000
Only the person I love.

51
00:03:28,500 --> 00:03:33,500
"Deep In"
(Episode 8)

52
00:03:33,786 --> 00:03:35,586
We've got other work
to do, everyone leave.

53
00:03:35,633 --> 00:03:36,953
Who am I responsible to?

54
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:39,480
Only the person I love.

55
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,880
Everyone, please disperse.

56
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:45,080
Well, it shouldn't be you.

57
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:47,960
It can't be you, bro.

58
00:03:48,640 --> 00:03:50,880
Fan service is enough.

59
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:53,240
Don't catch feelings under any circumstance.

60
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:01,360
Wu, finally you are here.

61
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:02,880
Talk some sense into Zhun.

62
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,360
Zhen Xin must have bewitched him.

63
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:05,400
He's lost it.

64
00:04:08,200 --> 00:04:09,200
You okay?

65
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:10,720
I'm fine.

66
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,600
How is he?

67
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,680
Are reporters still blocking him?

68
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:16,120
He's at the hotel.

69
00:04:16,640 --> 00:04:17,760
His private doctor went too.

70
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:19,120
Private doctor?

71
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,000
What's wrong with him?

72
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,000
Acute gastroenteritis.

73
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,640
Zhao Chen said it's nothing serious.

74
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:25,880
He's on an IV.

75
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:28,120
He's safe for now.

76
00:04:28,640 --> 00:04:29,360
But later,
they'll need a press conference.

77
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,160
It's my stomach.

78
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:32,320
I'm willing.

79
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:36,880
Where are you going?

80
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,240
To see him.

81
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:39,680
Calm down.

82
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:41,360
Outside the hotel,

83
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:42,480
reporters are everywhere.

84
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,600
I don't care.

85
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,160
I want to see him.

86
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:46,520
I can't wait another second.

87
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:48,240
Let me go.

88
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,600
I...

89
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:52,040
I'm in love with him.

90
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,160
Zhang Zhun.

91
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:55,600
Wake the fuck up.

92
00:04:56,520 --> 00:04:57,080
"Love"

93
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,960
isn't a word you throw around.

94
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:01,000
You're both men.

95
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:02,920
Can you be a little realistic?

96
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,360
What if the company finds out?

97
00:05:06,640 --> 00:05:08,440
How will you survive in this industry?

98
00:05:09,520 --> 00:05:10,520
Fine.

99
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,680
Even if

100
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:13,000
I let you go,

101
00:05:13,520 --> 00:05:14,600
what are you going as?

102
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:16,000
Zhang Zhun.

103
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,160
As myself.

104
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,360
You...

105
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,760
This time I'm not fine.

106
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,240
Something is wrong.

107
00:05:23,080 --> 00:05:24,080
In and out of the show,

108
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:25,760
I fell for him.

109
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,240
Senior.

110
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:33,360
Let me be selfish once.

111
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,240
Zhun.

112
00:05:44,080 --> 00:05:44,520
Fuck.

113
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:46,080
Zhun.

114
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:49,280
You did that on purpose.

115
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:52,080
Of course not.

116
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:54,800
We just got caught.

117
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,000
I had to admit it.

118
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:57,600
Or what?

119
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:59,760
Should I tell them we broke up,

120
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,440
and you climbed into a man's bed?

121
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:03,520
No.

122
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:04,840
I need to see him.

123
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:06,320
Are you out of your mind?

124
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,480
The reporters are still out there.

125
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:10,600
Want him labeled the male homewrecker?

126
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:17,400
Can't you hold back?

127
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:20,080
Play around in the show, fine.

128
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:21,800
But once it's over?

129
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,440
Move in and play house?

130
00:06:26,280 --> 00:06:27,440
Mr. Zhang seems decent.

131
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:29,160
Don't ruin him.

132
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,600
I'm not playing.

133
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:32,960
I want to announce our breakup.

134
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:34,440
Fine.

135
00:06:34,840 --> 00:06:36,000
All in the same line of work.

136
00:06:36,520 --> 00:06:37,520
I don't want to ruin you.

137
00:06:38,280 --> 00:06:39,280
But

138
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:41,080
my price is high.

139
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,320
Maybe hold on a bit longer?

140
00:06:51,840 --> 00:06:52,840
Who's that?

141
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,480
He looks familiar.

142
00:06:56,760 --> 00:06:57,760
Mr. Zhang.

143
00:06:58,280 --> 00:06:59,280
Come in,

144
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,200
Mr. Zhang.

145
00:07:01,553 --> 00:07:03,153
Mr. Zhang is the film's other male lead.

146
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:04,360
Stop filming.

147
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:05,720
You really came.

148
00:07:06,520 --> 00:07:07,040
Sorry.

149
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,640
I didn't mean to provoke you.

150
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:10,320
I just

151
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,120
wanted to see him.

152
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,680
The doctor said

153
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:14,720
it's nothing serious.

154
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:15,920
He just ate too spicy

155
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,120
and hurt his stomach.

156
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,000
You came empty-handed?

157
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:28,160
What?

158
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:29,400
Should I have brought fruit?

159
00:07:38,960 --> 00:07:39,960
You came late,

160
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:42,080
and brought nothing.

161
00:07:49,810 --> 00:07:51,616
Come and tell me your dream, Mr. Gao.

162
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,240
See?

163
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:57,080
You can accept other people's touch.

164
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,560
No.

165
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:02,120
Only yours.

166
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:10,080
Did you forget your line?

167
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,040
You're supposed to say,

168
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,240
I can hear your heartbeat.

169
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:16,840
Can you hear mine?

170
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:23,920
Honey.

171
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:25,240
Keep rehearsing.

172
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:26,960
I'll get you some milk.

173
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,840
She knows.

174
00:08:40,920 --> 00:08:41,920
Help me.

175
00:08:43,040 --> 00:08:44,040
I feel awful.

176
00:08:46,040 --> 00:08:47,040
Is your stomach hurting?

177
00:08:53,760 --> 00:08:54,760
Zhen Xin.

178
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:55,960
Where the fuck does it hurt?

179
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,600
Everywhere.

180
00:08:57,880 --> 00:08:58,320
Hurry.

181
00:08:58,520 --> 00:08:59,520
Help me.

182
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:02,160
You...

183
00:09:04,640 --> 00:09:05,920
Why are you so horny?

184
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:20,600
Aren't martial artists strict
about this stuff?

185
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,280
Why get your ears pierced?

186
00:09:25,560 --> 00:09:26,560
Just...

187
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,200
Pretty.

188
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:32,840
It is pretty.

189
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:41,600
You're on an IV.

190
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:43,680
Behave.

191
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:51,440
Zhun.

192
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,200
I'm glad you came.

193
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,000
Honey.

194
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,600
Done rehearsing?

195
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:10,760
I still have something to do.

196
00:10:10,920 --> 00:10:11,920
I'll go first.

197
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,200
I'll walk you out.

198
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:18,040
Take care of yourself.

199
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:33,680
Your taste

200
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:35,680
is still excellent.

201
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:39,160
Thanks.

202
00:10:40,560 --> 00:10:41,720
I don't want to wait anymore.

203
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:43,960
Me neither.

204
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,240
Spill.

205
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:48,120
How much?

206
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:49,720
What terms?

207
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,440
Fifty million.

208
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:53,240
Plus one movie.

209
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:54,480
Two S-tier dramas.

210
00:10:55,640 --> 00:10:56,960
Big-budget, TV-aired productions.

211
00:10:57,480 --> 00:10:58,600
At least second female lead.

212
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:00,600
Fifty million?

213
00:11:01,800 --> 00:11:02,800
You're worth that price?

214
00:11:04,800 --> 00:11:07,126
It's him... who's probably worth it.

215
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:12,400
Fine.

216
00:11:13,880 --> 00:11:15,040
I'll wire it in installments.

217
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:17,680
But we can't go public yet.

218
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:19,480
Thanks to you, Honey,

219
00:11:19,880 --> 00:11:21,720
this luxury car deal is rare.

220
00:11:22,160 --> 00:11:23,160
Give it a few more days.

221
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:24,920
What luxury car wants you?

222
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:26,960
One made for mistresses?

223
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,440
Say one more word,

224
00:11:28,640 --> 00:11:29,800
and it's another ten million.

225
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:34,240
How many days do I wait?

226
00:11:35,520 --> 00:11:36,960
The brand hasn't confirmed yet.

227
00:11:37,880 --> 00:11:38,880
But

228
00:11:39,160 --> 00:11:40,160
you know me.

229
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,560
I won't delay your business.

230
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:43,480
If needed,

231
00:11:44,040 --> 00:11:45,160
I can even help you.

232
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:46,440
Neither of us

233
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:48,080
wants to burn bridges.

234
00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:49,400
Right?

235
00:11:51,560 --> 00:11:53,000
The sooner, the better.

236
00:11:57,280 --> 00:11:58,720
Normally, with Mr. Zhen's situation,

237
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:00,080
we'd pause for a few more days.

238
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:02,000
But we're short on time.

239
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,480
The crew can't just sit around.

240
00:12:03,680 --> 00:12:04,680
So we resume today.

241
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:06,120
Got it.

242
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:07,240
Is Mr. Zhen better?

243
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:08,600
Can he shoot?

244
00:12:09,040 --> 00:12:09,480
Look.

245
00:12:09,880 --> 00:12:10,880
There he is.

246
00:12:12,880 --> 00:12:13,400
Mr. Zhen.

247
00:12:13,520 --> 00:12:14,600
You recovered fast.

248
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:17,376
Someone was concerned about me.

249
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:17,800
Director Zhou.

250
00:12:18,013 --> 00:12:18,853
I'd naturally heal faster.
Here you are.

251
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:19,920
Mr. Zhang.
Director Zhou.

252
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:20,960
Hey.

253
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,000
Mr. Zhen.

254
00:12:22,040 --> 00:12:23,040
Let's rehearse first.

255
00:12:24,040 --> 00:12:24,800
In this scene,

256
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:27,040
Fang Chi brings Gao
Zhun to a bar as a reward.

257
00:12:27,640 --> 00:12:28,720
Then someone hits on him,

258
00:12:28,760 --> 00:12:30,120
asks Gao Zhun for his number,

259
00:12:30,400 --> 00:12:31,680
and sends a hookup message.

260
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:33,560
Fang Chi gets furious.

261
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:35,360
So he leaves with Gao Zhun.

262
00:12:35,640 --> 00:12:37,920
Later, he comes back,
saying he forgot his glasses,

263
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:39,120
and beats the guy up.

264
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:41,080
AD.

265
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,440
Is the guy here?

266
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:43,600
Hey?

267
00:12:44,160 --> 00:12:45,160
Tommy.

268
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:45,680
Tommy.

269
00:12:45,880 --> 00:12:46,880
I'm here~

270
00:12:47,880 --> 00:12:48,880
Hi~

271
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:52,200
Let's rehearse then.

272
00:12:52,920 --> 00:12:53,920
OK~

273
00:12:54,160 --> 00:12:54,880
Let's run it once.

274
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:56,440
Later, say to Mr. Zhang,

275
00:12:56,760 --> 00:12:58,080
"Hey, handsome. Got a boyfriend?"

276
00:12:58,280 --> 00:12:59,720
Then follow your feeling.

277
00:13:00,280 --> 00:13:01,480
Mr. Zhang, just act naturally.

278
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:03,840
Let's run it.

279
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:05,360
Okay.

280
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,200
Hey, handsome~
Yes, that's it.

281
00:13:07,880 --> 00:13:08,560
Got a boyfriend?~

282
00:13:08,800 --> 00:13:10,000
Sir, don't touch his chest.

283
00:13:10,040 --> 00:13:11,240
Put your hand on his shoulder.

284
00:13:12,160 --> 00:13:12,960
Not his chest?

285
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,000
I can't feel it that way.

286
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:16,359
That's not my character.

287
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:16,840
Fine, fine.

288
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:18,360
We'll do it your way.

289
00:13:19,880 --> 00:13:21,040
Mr. Zhen, got a light?

290
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:28,320
Hey, handsome~

291
00:13:28,400 --> 00:13:29,880
Got a boyfriend?~

292
00:13:30,920 --> 00:13:31,960
Too much, sir.

293
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:32,520
Huh?

294
00:13:32,920 --> 00:13:34,760
How do you feel about this extra scene?

295
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:38,320
Not bad.

296
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,000
Which film school?

