00:32:54,760 --> 00:32:55,760
Let go.

597
00:32:58,760 --> 00:32:59,760
Sir.

598
00:32:59,960 --> 00:33:01,520
Do you think teasing me like this

599
00:33:01,800 --> 00:33:02,800
is fun?

600
00:33:03,640 --> 00:33:04,680
Then as you wish,

601
00:33:05,440 --> 00:33:06,760
I'm hooked.

602
00:33:07,600 --> 00:33:08,600
Let go of me.

603
00:37:06,680 --> 00:37:07,000
Hey.

604
00:37:07,400 --> 00:37:08,400
Honestly, Zhang Zhun,

605
00:37:08,680 --> 00:37:10,016
I didn't know you could act this well.

606
00:37:10,040 --> 00:37:11,160
I underestimated you before.

607
00:37:11,200 --> 00:37:11,600
No hard feelings.

608
00:37:12,040 --> 00:37:13,120
You're too kind, Mr. Jiang.

609
00:37:13,280 --> 00:37:13,800
If this film works,

610
00:37:14,080 --> 00:37:15,656
we should thank Chairman
Jiang for investing.

611
00:37:15,680 --> 00:37:16,160
Come on.

612
00:37:16,560 --> 00:37:17,480
You're so modest,

613
00:37:17,520 --> 00:37:18,680
you're making me embarrassed.

614
00:37:19,280 --> 00:37:20,280
With you all in it,

615
00:37:20,360 --> 00:37:21,480
the box office is safe.

616
00:37:23,840 --> 00:37:24,840
That candy...

617
00:37:44,880 --> 00:37:46,400
The way he stared at it just now,

618
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:48,896
didn't he look like a black
panther watching prey?

619
00:37:48,920 --> 00:37:49,960
I almost didn't dare move.

620
00:37:51,040 --> 00:37:52,040
He

621
00:37:52,560 --> 00:37:53,560
gets like that sometimes.

622
00:37:59,880 --> 00:38:00,880
The way you look at him

623
00:38:01,080 --> 00:38:02,080
is interesting too.

624
00:38:03,480 --> 00:38:04,480
Like what?

625
00:38:06,760 --> 00:38:07,760
Hard to say.

626
00:38:08,840 --> 00:38:09,840
A leopard cat.

627
00:38:10,520 --> 00:38:11,520
Alert,

628
00:38:12,200 --> 00:38:13,200
but unable to look away.
